        <div class="chapter-num">Chapter I</div>
        <h2>Mississippi</h2>
        <p class="chapter-dek">The flood that made the land, the crop that ran the economy, and the lines — drawn by rivers and by lenders — that still shape where people live.</p>
        <div class="photo-slot">
          <div class="ph-label">Chapter opener — image</div>
