        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:26px; margin:44px 0 14px;">Cultural geography</h3>
        <p class="body-p">[Section: how the plantation-era land pattern — large holdings, few towns, dispersed labor housing — still governs where schools, clinics, and grocery stores sit today. Reference redlining and postwar lending patterns that concentrated Black land loss.]</p>
