            <div class="tm-label">Population at its height, now roughly 500</div>
            <div class="tm-source">Source: Visit Cleveland MS / heritage museum</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="body-p">Assimilation was never simple: under Jim Crow's binary racial order, Chinese families were classified as neither Black nor white, and the 1927 Gong Lum v. Rice case — brought by a Delta family barred from a white school — reached the U.S. Supreme Court. [Continue: identity, language retention, Lucky Eleven events, the "Delta Wok" oral-history/recipe project at Delta State.]</p>
